description: Returns a list of registration tokens for the specified extension(s).

parameters.name: Type
parameters.description: The kind of extension. Conditional: You must specify either TypeName and Type, or Arn.

parameters.name: TypeName
parameters.description: The name of the extension. Conditional: You must specify either TypeName and Type, or Arn.

parameters.name: TypeArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the extension. Conditional: You must specify either TypeName and Type, or Arn.

parameters.name: RegistrationStatusFilter
parameters.description: The current status of the extension registration request. The default is IN_PROGRESS.

nested_items.name: RegistrationTokenList
nested_items.description: A list of extension registration tokens.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If the request doesn't return all the remaining results, NextToken is set to a token. To retrieve the next set of results, call this action again and assign that token to the request object's NextToken parameter. If the request returns all results, NextToken is set to null.
